item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - 1989 (Taylor's Version) & 1989 (Taylor's Version) [Deluxe in M4A iTunes Format
item.description:
Can someone give me the link of 1989 (Taylor's Version) and the DELUXE—the updated master on November 6 in M4A iTunes format? They say the original album's master is defective due to buzz/electronic noise, it was replaced with a digital version, although not completely fixed, and the new version is now available. Thank you in advance! ✨
